# {{REPO_NAME}} — repo inbox

> **Durable, append-only.** Bidirectional message thread for this
> repo. The orchestrator and the sub-kit (and humans) leave notes
> here for each other. Read on session start; never regenerated.
>
> **Different from `/inbox`** — that's per-person. This is per-repo:
> messages addressed to "whoever's working in {{REPO_NAME}} right
> now."
>
> **Format:** ISO-8601 UTC timestamp, sender, subject, body. New
> entries on top.

